The ship's computer announced that it had picked up unidentifiable 
signals at extreme ranges.

Tyrael's mind reeled at that. Could it be? Surely, it had to be the 
Preds... Which meant they had to get on the defensive. Now.

Tyrael: Cheetah! In the base now! We'll analyze it later! Battle 
stations for now!

He lowered the shields and entered the base.
